Darmstadt is well-connected by public transport and easy to reach from major German cities.  
There is a direct connection from **Frankfurt International Airport (FRA)** to Darmstadt by train or bus.

As travel conditions in Germany can be affected by occasional airport or rail disruptions, we recommend planning a small buffer.

